{"tid":422703,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"家姐帶隻狗公上黎食團圓飯，有咩要注意？","createTime":"2017-10-03T09:51:50.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-03T14:57:32.000Z","uid":54760,"like":6,"dislike":73,"uniUserReply":46,"replies":[{"pid":"066e2eb46a4c7f9614aecb17dea0c2c4f57eed38","tid":422703,"uid":54760,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T09:51:50.000Z","msg":"家姐前排見返個細個識嘅男仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n個男仔拎左我家姐電話就瘋狂flirt<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n過程中仲話其實鐘意左我家姐十幾年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n果時我家姐仲有男朋友，但就冷戰緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n咁個男仔就趁呢段時間乘虛而入 噓寒問暖咁樣討得我家姐歡心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n今晚屋企食團圓飯，家姐突然話要帶果個男仔上黎食飯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但係我角度黎睇，團圓飯係同屋企人食飯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n你講話係男朋友都還可以接受，但果個男仔淨係熟左無耐，仲要唔係男朋友身份<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n大家覺得今餐飯要點做好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c4cc3baa92a0e61d6e0e180663fc906b5556fd6","tid":422703,"uid":54760,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T09:52:37.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b05085792fb8924c78c27045ac90dde680e3fdc","tid":422703,"uid":68081,"like":9,"dislike":5,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T09:52:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>家姐前排見返個細個識嘅男仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n個男仔拎左我家姐電話就瘋狂flirt<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n過程中仲話其實鐘意左我家姐十幾年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n果時我家姐仲有男朋友，但就冷戰緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gi